data.description: Fully renovated with custom features and personality! This is not a cookie cutter home. Escape the city, enjoy wildlife in every corner of your home, lots of windows with natural lighting. Double doors, Gourmet brand new kitchen with quartz countertops, upgraded modern cabinets, stainless steel appliances, chefs kitchen with 2 ovens, freestanding oven and micro. New AC system & garage. Huge Living room with high ceilings, gas log fireplace with wood mantel and built-ins cabinets. Large formal dining room with plenty of windows. New floors all through the house, include wood/vinyl flooring, porcelain and carpet for bedrooms. Huge soaking tub in master bedroom . Shower & separate tub. House sits in the middle of a quiet acreage, Ideal for nature lovers. Sprinkler system. Detached garage/shop area and well house adds approximate 800 sq ft.. Full serviced generator & 500 gal propane tank system. Home sits peacefully on 3.13 acres !! 10min from Lake Jackson. No HOA, Horses Allowed!
